  "texts": [
    "We are not claiming that these results should be taken to mean practitioners should always use MR-Hydra and/or HC2.",
    "There are strengths and weakness to all the algorithms we have described.",
    "Indeed, there is a case to be made for using QUANT by default, at least for exploratory analysis, because it is so fast.",
    "Understanding when it is appropriate to use which algorithm for a specific problem is an active research area.",
    "However, we suggest that, in the absence of any prior information these two algorithms make a sensible starting point for a new TSC problem."
